content.text:
找到问题了！看配置现状：

**Bindings 设定的是：** QQ Bot bot1/bot2/bot3 → **Father** ✅

**但是 agents list 里只配了 son，没有 father 和 spirit！**

```json
"bindings": [
  { "type": "route", "agentId": "father", "match": { "channel": "qqbot", "accountId": "bot1" } },
  { "type": "route", "agentId": "father", "match": { "channel": "qqbot", "accountId": "bot2" } },
  { "type": "route", "agentId": "father", "match": { "channel": "qqbot", "accountId": "bot3" } }
]

"agents": { "list": [ { "id": "son" } ] }  ← 只有 son，没有 father 和 spirit
```

所以现在实际上是：**QQ Bot 消息本该走 Father → 但 father 没注册 → 不知道为啥 fallback 到 son 了**，导致你看到的是 son 而不是 Faye。

要修的话，需要在 agents list 里加上 father 和 spirit：

```json
"agents": { "list": [
  { "id": "father", 
    "model": { "primary": "deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash" } 
  },
  { "id": "spirit",
    "model": { "primary": "deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash" }
  },
  { "id": "son",
    "model": { "primary": "deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash" }
  }
]}
```

要不要我直接改 openclaw.json 把 father 和 spirit 补上？这样下次你就是跟 Faye（father）聊天，son 和 spirit 只作为 spawn 的子代理跑。

